name: Louis Bay
description: I am a fun loving person who enjoys life, loves to laugh, works and plays hard. For me life is about enjoying the moments and being with friends and family who have positive energy, and a great attitude. I am at a goodplace in my professional life, and am looking to find a similarly motivated, dynamic, and balanced woman. People tell me I am crazy fun and most women find me attractive, slightly glamorous, intellectually stimulating, and a high energy soul.
